list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Implemented the `sortDeckInNumberOrder()` method - CardGame.java: - Added the new method using the `Collections` class's method `sort()`
- Card.java: - Implemented the Comparable interface, and the `compareTo()` method to support the `Collections.sort()` method in CardGame.java
- Main.java: - Called the `sortDeckInNumberOrder()` and `getDeck()` to check that the cards were sorted
- Also, having to rebuild .idea folder, there are a number of files changes associated with it
